name: Trees, Lots of Trees
description:
Invest in the future of Earth. Plant trees, lots of trees.
Climate Change is a clear and present danger.
Tomorrow is too late for us, our kids, and the new generations.
Let’s do the simplest, and one of the most effective actions – plant trees, lots of trees.
payDisclosure: There is always a risk in any investment. You are investing to save the planet one tree at a time. We are super confident and would like to thank you.
